How to play

Arrow <UP>		--> Thrust
Arrow <LEFT>	--> Turn left
Arrow <RIGHT>	--> Turn right
Arrow <DOWN>	--> Turn down
Spacebar		--> Auto thrust
Shift			--> Toggle drifting

-- more to come after adding collisions --

# Spaceship-mirrored
Control one spaceship and the rest are mirrored.

